{"tid":406892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制陣營批評何君堯「幫倒忙」","createTime":"2017-09-20T04:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T18:02:01.000Z","uid":5195,"like":176,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"042bb21b782b34b58293c7b4fb5173cd33dfb2b6","tid":406892,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"明報文章】立法會議員何君堯周日在添馬公園發起「反港獨、反冷血、反偽學吶喊大會」，據了解，何君堯事前興致勃勃廣邀建制派參與，但建制派主流意見認為此時不應搞「批鬥式」集會，免令社會更分化，所以大部分人以不在香港、事忙等理由推卻，新民黨主席葉劉淑儀更力勸何君堯無謂搞，然而何君堯一意孤行，終掀起對港獨者「殺無赦」的言論風波。建制陣營中有人批評何君堯「幫倒忙」，並為泛民提供攻擊的「彈藥」。"},{"pid":"6cce3cb2d053bab0e5fca916845607b306ae027e","tid":406892,"uid":39012,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:31:40.000Z","msg":"咁快就棄卒"},{"pid":"f50862cf10e6950874a30f93127b49789f567113","tid":406892,"uid":123248,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:33:10.000Z","msg":"正所謂唔怕神一樣既對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd78bc6a22a41169fe3e4b8d283cffeafa9ac1d","tid":406892,"uid":32221,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁快就棄卒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢自己攞黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔係唔知隊友近幾年玩開以言入罪<br />\n呢啲豬隊友唔而家賣幾時賣？<br />\n賣完仲企到法治高地<br />\n俾港豬一視同仁假象"},{"pid":"ae9a9aaf48ea46f3b8c640dbccfec505fad6858a","tid":406892,"uid":96760,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T05:02:31.000Z","msg":"乜嘢幫倒忙吖，根本佢個角色設定就係咁，吸啲激進廢老／大中華膠票"},{"pid":"0efe3e62a1db5a11269aed5db26dbfabe210eb29","tid":406892,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街何生係咪自己友黎 卧卧底？"},{"pid":"5a5108957c563f